text:
Udi Udi Jaye - Raees Udi Udi Jaye Video from Shahrukh Khan and Mahira Khan starrer Raees Udi Udi Jaye Lyrics from Raees starring Shah Rukh Khan & Mahira Khan. The song is sung by Sukhwinder Singh, Bhoomi Trivedi & Karsan Sagathia, has music produced by Ram Sampath while lyrics are penned by Javed Akhtar. Udi Udi Jaye Lyrics 
Arey udi udi udi… udi jaye.. 
Udi udi jaye 
Kehne ko toh khel hai Ye tera mera sanjha Par mera dil hai patang Aur teri nazar manjha 
Manjhe se lipti ye patang Judi judi jaaye 
Do dil ude, do dil ude Unche aasmaano mein jude (x2) 
(Udi udi jaye) 
Mujhe kab tha pata iska Tere prem ka iktaara Mann mein yun pal pal baajega 
Mujhe kab thi khabar iski Mere mann ke singhasan par tu Sada ko yun tu birajega 
Koi bhi kathinayi ho ya koi ho majburi Teri meri ek bhi pal hove nahi doori 
Manjhe se lipti ye patang Judi judi jaye
